00:17:29,960 --> 00:17:31,320
<i>Karena ada sesuatu
yang harus kuketahui.</i>

146
00:17:31,320 --> 00:17:32,290
<i>Apa itu?</i>

147
00:17:32,290 --> 00:17:35,340
<i>Itu bukti yang
akan membuktikan...</i>

148
00:17:35,340 --> 00:17:40,650
